# Unity .gitignore — 来自官方模板
# https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Unity.gitignore
# 建议按需从 Global/ 补充编辑器与系统规则：https://github.com/github/gitignore/tree/main/Global
#
.utmp/
/[Ll]ibrary/
/[Tt]emp/
/[Oo]bj/
/[Bb]uild/
/[Bb]uilds/
/[Ll]ogs/
/[Uu]ser[Ss]ettings/
*.log

# Blender 辅助文件
*.blend1
*.blend1.meta

# MemoryCaptures 体积大且可能含敏感数据
/[Mm]emory[Cc]aptures/

# 录制文件体积大
/[Rr]ecordings/

# 若需忽略 Asset Store 工具插件，取消下一行注释
# /[Aa]ssets/AssetStoreTools*

# JetBrains Rider 插件（自动生成）
/[Aa]ssets/Plugins/Editor/JetBrains*
*.DotSettings.user

# Visual Studio
.vs/

# Gradle
.gradle/

# 各 IDE 生成的工程文件
ExportedObj/
.consulo/
*.csproj
*.unityproj
*.sln
*.slnx
*.suo
*.tmp
*.user
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svd
*.pdb
*.mdb
*.opendb
*.VC.db

# Unity3D 生成的 meta
*.pidb.meta
*.pdb.meta
*.mdb.meta

# 崩溃报告
sysinfo.txt

# Mono 崩溃转储
mono_crash.*

# 构建产物扩展名
*.apk
*.aab
*.unitypackage
*.unitypackage.meta
*.app

# Crashlytics
crashlytics-build.properties

# Test Runner 临时场景
InitTestScene*.unity*

# Addressables（默认忽略，可按项目再调整）
/ServerData
/[Aa]ssets/StreamingAssets/aa*
/[Aa]ssets/AddressableAssetsData/link.xml*
/[Aa]ssets/Addressables_Temp*
/[Aa]ssets/AddressableAssetsData/*/*.bin*

# Visual Scripting 生成文件
/[Aa]ssets/Unity.VisualScripting.Generated/VisualScripting.Flow/UnitOptions.db
/[Aa]ssets/Unity.VisualScripting.Generated/VisualScripting.Flow/UnitOptions.db.meta
/[Aa]ssets/Unity.VisualScripting.Generated/VisualScripting.Core/Property Providers
/[Aa]ssets/Unity.VisualScripting.Generated/VisualScripting.Core/Property Providers.meta

# Play Mode 测试自动生成场景
/[Aa]ssets/[Ii]nit[Tt]est[Ss]cene*.unity*

# Assets 下自动缓存
/[Aa]ssets/[Ss]ceneDependencyCache*

# --- 以下为常用系统/桌面垃圾文件（非 Unity 官方模板内，便于 Windows/macOS 协作）---
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
